OL,3,CSuspended Labour MP Mike Amesbury to
OL,4,Cbe sentenced for punching man in street
OL,6,FSuspended Labour MP Mike Amesbury will
OL,7,Fbe sentenced for punching a man
OL,8,Ffollowing a row in the street.
OL,10,FThe Runcorn and Helsby MP, who has
OL,11,Fbeen sitting as an independent since
OL,12,Fhe was suspended following his arrest
OL,13,Fin October last year, is due to appear
OL,14,Fat Chester Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,FHe pleaded guilty at a hearing in
OL,18,FJanuary to assaulting 45-year-old Paul
OL,19,FFellows in Main Street in Frodsham,
OL,20,FCheshire, in the early hours of
OL,21,FOctober 26.
