OL,3,CSuspended Labour MP Mike Amesbury to
OL,4,Cbe sentenced for punching man in street
OL,6,FThe court heard the sentencing
OL,7,Fguidelines for the offence ranged from
OL,8,Fa high level community order up to a
OL,9,Fprison sentence.
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Tan Ikram told Amesbury
OL,12,Fhe was "leaving all options open at
OL,13,Fthis stage".
OL,15,FSpeaking outside court after entering
OL,16,Fhis guilty plea, Amesbury said: "I'm
OL,17,Fsincerely sorry to Mr Fellows and his
OL,18,Ffamily."
