OL,6,FSpeaking after the MP's last court
OL,7,Fhearing, a Labour Party spokesman
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is right that Mike Amesbury
OL,9,Fhas taken responsibility for his
OL,10,Funacceptable actions.
OL,12,F"He was rightly suspended by the
OL,13,FLabour Party following the
OL,14,Fannouncement of the police
OL,15,Finvestigation. We cannot comment
OL,16,Ffurther whilst legal proceedings are
OL,17,Fstill ongoing."
